\n<br />\n轉台睇新聞試過，電話like page試過，都係冇改變，咁就唔好改，冇得救<br />\n<br />\n再講唔通下下都爆佢地咩，對件事無好處<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唯有死忍，深藍個個比我爆到唔出聲就算，淺藍觀念錯還錯唔會仆街到深藍咁離譜，由佢講"},{"pid":"d1770815d3b818b50741d1e53b752da0e611e53c","tid":1593523,"uid":45958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f452a86ef3da7c3ada6c1db5f63e3d4a3a1d0aca","tid":1593523,"uid":288093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ca4ddf2e161a30c7a4f8cda0a6a316bae202cb03","tid":1593523,"uid":45958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"db866d5db4e3c36388a477298390302ce6ef1639","tid":1593523,"uid":288093,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T15:48:17.000Z","msg":"政見唔同就不孝？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無禮無家孝係講緊你同佢地辯論時嘅態度？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T15:49:20.000Z","msg":"講我facebook發表嘅言論....."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T15:56:40.000Z","msg":"咁慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />fb打嘅野都要被評為不孝<br />\n不過我個兩舊老古董就無fb，如果唔係應該會激到佢地仆哂街<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T15:58:05.000Z","msg":"成日話我打粗口又盛喎"},{"pid":"f61ade429a101d032c8fdef1fac03c3bcd99bcdf","tid":1593523,"uid":316643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T15:58:19.000Z","msg":"same"},{"pid":"770b1525911104c9f500f5601d4506605ab0e727","tid":1593523,"uid":270956,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"050071c055836af39b946674a31f4bb435614e46","tid":1593523,"uid":45958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8bcc97fdc68eae8a77355f55926c215146f35c5c","tid":1593523,"uid":270956,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T15:35:35.000Z","msg":"我屋企人都係，淺藍成日話自己中立。<br />\n認為總之暴力就唔啱，警察都有好人、都係職責所在為生計無辦法 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T15:37:54.000Z","msg":"屌我老豆老母都係咁講，點破解好"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T15:58:59.000Z","msg":"示威者好暴力：有無瞭解前因後果？正正因為和平無用，示威者先升級採取更激進嘅手法。更何況示威者同警察、黑社會、藍絲、福建幫武力根本不對等，如果你譴責暴力，更應該譴責個班警察、黑社會、藍絲、福建幫。破壞閘機、放火都只係傷害死物，同示威者被砍、被射爆眼，甚至可能俾打死相比，人命定死物更重要？<br />\n<br />\n警察都有好人：我信可能有好人，但好人已經一早全部走曬啦。喺呢個制度底下，全部警察只會被同化一齊同流合污。我唔信佢地唔做警察無其他選擇，一樣可以揀做其他工作。唔係為咗錢可以埋沒良知，無底線，做咩都得，甚至殺人。"},{"pid":"cb19912db28bd708a375f20e0a0af84c6a12c72d","tid":1593523,"uid":288093,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bf66827f2b2c20dff8d61cd7515f79275bd0aef6","tid":1593523,"uid":45958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"602a2e653ea592cb77a5e381c0e0df960f439930","tid":1593523,"uid":288093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d151118bb9aa943b550883260c85c3ee66d2cac0","tid":1593523,"uid":45958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T15:44:33.000Z","msg":"因為要還，廢事整壞麻撚煩"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T15:48:48.000Z","msg":"幾時到期<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T15:49:36.000Z","msg":"有撚排呀屌"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T15:59:00.000Z","msg":"如果reset部機好似要重新登入<br />\n如果佢地識唔識登入，你又扮唔記得個Ac，咁得唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99d07e63c45836d76896884e9b5e45705fa9b118","tid":1593523,"uid":321719,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T15:59:33.000Z","msg":"大撚把，不用寂莫"}]}